DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates the potential conflict that can occur when nesting theme providers with styled-components. When a custom theme is provided inside a BladeProvider, the shallow merge behavior can override critical theme tokens needed by Blade components.

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
